Hi!
I'm Sebi

And i am a passionate developer.

About me
Who am i?
I am a motivated and hardworking individual with great passion for coding and developing websites. I am currently in my first year of studying Computer Science at university. Last years i've worked on multiple projects, personal or paid and i achieved some of the programming skills necessary nowadays.

Anytime I have the opportunity to learn something new, I won't miss it. I am currently available for a job opportunity and searching for a summer internship experience. Some things about my projects: fast, responsive, attractive, dynamic.
